    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Stonk Hodler is a one button stock trading incremental game about behavior finance. You hold down the button, then when you feel like it, release the button to sell.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3160070/extras/d19ceb04f3b34f246bfaeca618b1390f.poster.avif?t=1769717899\" width=480 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3160070/extras/d19ceb04f3b34f246bfaeca618b1390f.webm?t=1769717899\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3160070/extras/d19ceb04f3b34f246bfaeca618b1390f.mp4?t=1769717899\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Now, go make yourself a trillionaire.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The loss? Don't worry about them for now.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Developer Note</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Please don't use this as a guidance for investment. I mean, you do yourself, not that I can stop you.</p>",
